"title": "2427: gospel, transmission of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2427: gospel, transmission of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The gospel has been passed down through the NT witness to Jesus Christ, through the proclamation of the good news about Jesus Christ, and through the providential guidance of the Holy Spirit.</p>\n<h2>The NT witness to Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>The events of Jesus Christ's life were carefully recorded</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:1-Luke1:4\">LUK 1:1–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:24\">JHN 21:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:1-Acts1:2\">ACT 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h2>The apostles bore witness to the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:8\">1CO 15:3–15:8</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:16\">2PE 1:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:4\">1JN 1:1–1:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:45-Luke24:48\">LUK 24:45–24:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:27\">JHN 15:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:8\">ACT 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:21-Acts1:22\">ACT 1:21–1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:32\">ACT 2:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts4:1-Acts4:20\">ACT 4:1–4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:32\">ACT 5:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:30-Acts13:31\">ACT 13:30–13:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3-Heb2:4\">HEB 2:3–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:1\">1PE 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:14\">1JN 4:14</a></p>\n<h2>The proclamation of the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:14-Rom10:15\">ROM 10:14–10:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:1-1Cor15:2\">1CO 15:1–15:2</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:8-Eph3:9\">EPH 3:8–3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:12\">ACT 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:21\">1CO 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:23\">GAL 1:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:2\">2TI 4:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:7\">HEB 13:7</a></p>\n<h2>The guidance of the Holy Spirit in the transmission of the gospel</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:26\">JHN 14:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:26\">JHN 15:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:12-John16:15\">JHN 16:12–16:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:32\">ACT 5:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:3-Heb2:4\">HEB 2:3–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:6\">1JN 5:6</a></p>",
